WEBVTT

00:00:02.097 --> 00:00:06.569
The murder happened a little over 21 years ago,

00:00:06.569 --> 00:00:10.848
January the 18th, 1991,

00:00:10.848 --> 00:00:13.109
in a small

00:00:13.109 --> 00:00:15.483
bedroom community

00:00:15.483 --> 00:00:18.318
of Lynwood, California, just a few miles

00:00:18.318 --> 00:00:20.816
southeast of Los Angeles.

00:00:20.816 --> 00:00:23.651
A father came out of his house

00:00:23.651 --> 00:00:27.058
to tell his teenage son and his five friends

00:00:27.058 --> 00:00:29.837
that it was time for them to stop horsing around

00:00:29.837 --> 00:00:32.747
on the front lawn and on the sidewalk,